These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, pepper, eggplant, avocado
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, trance, pop, house
There are 4 different nationalities: german, chinese, japanese, argentine
4 different pets are kept: fish, lizard, ferret, dog
 1. the fan of country is on the right of the fan of trance##1
 2. the person eating pineapple is in an even position##4
 3. the german is on the left of the fan of pop##1
 4. the japanese is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
 5. the fan of country is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3
 6. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
 7. the chinese is the person eating eggplant##1
 8. the owner of the ferret is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the dog and the fan of house##2
10. the person eating pineapple is the owner of the dog##1
11. the fan of pop is the person eating avocado##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | eggplant  | pineapple    | avocado    | pepper   |
| Music-Genre   | trance     | country   | pop       | house    |
| Nationality   | chinese | german | argentine    | japanese |
| Pet           | lizard | dog       | fish | ferret     |

