.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: garlic, raspberry, pomegranate, pear
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, board-games, fishing, rock-climbing
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, egyptian, russian, brazilian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, skateboarding, tennis, baseball
 1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an even position##4
 2. the egyptian is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
 4. the person eating raspberry is the japanese##1
 5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
 6. the japanese is on the left or right of the russian##3
 7. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
 8. the brazilian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
 9. the russian is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating pomegranate is in an odd position##4
11. the russian is the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Food          | garlic  | raspberry    | pomegranate     | pear       |
| Hobby         | fishing | rock-climbing | puzzles   | board-games |
| Nationality   | russian | japanese   | egyptian   | brazilian    |
| Sport         | tennis | baseball  | rugby | skateboarding   |

