.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, fanta, coffee, water
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, dancer, pilot, electrician
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, malaysian, pakistani, american
4 different pets are kept: fish, ferret, horse, chinchilla
 1. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the firefighter##3
 2. the malaysian is the pilot##1
 3. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 4. the firefighter is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 5. the person drinking fanta is the electrician##1
 6. the person drinking water is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 7. the owner of the fish is the american##1
 8. the electrician is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the indian##1
10. the owner of the fish is the person drinking coffee##1
11. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | tea | coffee   | water    | fanta      |
| Job           | pilot | firefighter | dancer | electrician     |
| Nationality   | malaysian      | american   | indian   | pakistani |
| Pet           | chinchilla         | fish       | horse  | ferret       |

