.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, coffee, almond-milk, cola
There 4 different types of food: apricot, asparagus, nectarine, eggplant
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, filmmaking, writing, baking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, baseball, rowing, snowboarding
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is the person eating apricot##1
 2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 3. the person eating apricot is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
 4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an even position##4
 5. the person drinking coffee is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 6. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 7. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 8. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3
 9. the person who's sport is rowing is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
10. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
11. the person drinking almond-milk is the person eating eggplant##1
12. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the person eating apricot##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | cola       | almond-milk   | soy-milk   | coffee   |
| Food       | asparagus        | eggplant | apricot    | nectarine       |
| Hobby      | baking | filmmaking    | writing  | singing |
| Sport      | baseball  | rowing  | water-polo | snowboarding    |

