.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, watermelon, apricot, cabbage
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, video-games, reading, board-games
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, videographer, entrepreneur, dancer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, sailing, swimming, golf
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person eating cabbage##2
 3. the entrepreneur is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 4. the videographer is the person eating asparagus##1
 5. the freelancer is on the left or right of the videographer##3
 6. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an even position##4
 7. the person eating watermelon is the freelancer##1
 8. the person who's hobby is reading is the videographer##1
 9. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
10. the videographer is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
11. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person eating apricot##3
12. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Food    | apricot    | cabbage      | asparagus          | watermelon    |
| Hobby   | video-games | board-games       | reading | drawing |
| Job     | dancer     | entrepreneur      | videographer     | freelancer |
| Sport   | sailing   | golf | swimming        | parkour   |

