 3. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person eating kale##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
 5. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan of trance is between the italian and the fan of r&b##2
 7. the fan of blues is the person eating cucumber##1
 8. the person drinking cola is the person eating cucumber##1
 9. the mexican is on the far right##1
10. the japanese is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
