 1. the owner of the hamster is in an odd position##4
 2. the owner of the goat is between the owner of the hamster and the owner of the rabbit##2
 3. the russian is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 4. the person watching martial-arts movies is in an odd position##4
 5. the egyptian is on the right of the malaysian##1
 6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
 7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 8. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the argentine##1
 9. the owner of the goat is between the russian and the person watching documentary movies##2
10. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
11. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an even position##4
12. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
