The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, rugby, badminton, weightlifting
 1. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the fan of techno##1
 2. the person who's sport is badminton is in an even position##4
 3. the fan of funk is between the person watching superhero movies and the person who's sport is rugby##2
 4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
 5. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
 6. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
 7. the fan of techno is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person watching superhero movies##1
 9. the person eating artichoke is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
11. the person eating artichoke is on the far left or far right##3
12. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
13. the fan of classical is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |      4       |
