 3. the pilot is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
 4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the french##1
 5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 6. the pakistani is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
 8. the french is on the right of the pakistani##1
 9. the project-manager is on the left of the pilot##1
10. the accountant is in an even position##4
11. the american is the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
