.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, lemonade, mirinda
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, reading, filmmaking, magic-tricks
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, epic, family
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, baseball, basketball, rowing
 1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
 2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
 3. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 4. the person watching drama movies is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 7. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching epic movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
10. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
11. the person watching family movies is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | lemonade       | fanta | coffee        | mirinda        |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | filmmaking       | cooking | reading |
| Movie-Genre   | family     | drama        | crime    | epic      |
| Sport         | baseball     | basketball    | rowing | weightlifting   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, jazz, dubstep, blues
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, brazilian, british, chinese
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, badminton, climbing, skateboarding
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, scooter, tram, subway
 1. the fan of blues is the person who's sport is climbing##1
 2. the person who's sport is climbing is between the dutch and the chinese##2
 3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
 4. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the brazilian##1
 5. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
 6. the fan of jazz is the person who's sport is badminton##1
 7. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
 8. the chinese is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
10. the dutch is in an even position##4
11. the dutch is on the far right##1
12. the fan of gospel is on the right of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | jazz      | gospel | blues     | dubstep        |
| Nationality   | british | chinese  | brazilian     | dutch |
| Sport         | badminton    | golf | climbing      | skateboarding |
| Transport     | subway | scooter     | tram | boat       |

 